column5: Looking for suckers to cut up and use as bait for an upcoming lake trout trip . Does anyone know of a spot in the Dufferin County area that I could get a couple . PM me if you like , thanks !
Well you're on the right site. Tons of suckers on OFC.
Well you're on the right site. Tons of suckers on OFC.  Yep, they say there is one born every minute.
Ya , tons of suckers out there but not the ones I'm looking for !
